2001-04-29 20:50  juanco

	* private/juanco/todo_juanco.html: Updated juanco's todo

2001-04-29 20:44  juanco

	* src/: elements/StandardElements.pas, tasks/DelphiTasks.pas:
	Factored out element to attribute mapping functionality of <dcc>
	task into Attributes.pas so other tasks can use it.

2001-04-29 18:56  juanco

	* want.xml, make/bootstrap.bat, src/WantResources.pas,
	src/tasks/DelphiTasks.pas: Now most options to the <dcc> task can
	be specified both as attributes and elements. This allows for
	setting options conditionally, i.e.:
	
	  <dcc>
	    <optimize value="yes"  unless="DEBUG" />
	
	Updated build.xml to use new features.

2001-04-29 18:54  juanco

	* src/elements/PatternSets.pas: BUG: Concatenating base path to
	include/exclude patterns in Patternsets preventing generic patterns
	like **/CVS from matching everything they should.  Fixed.

2001-04-29 18:52  juanco

	* lib/: paszlib-1.0-dante-1.zip, paszlib-1.0.zip: Overflow checking
	in paszlib\zDeflate.pas produces an error. Patched.

2001-04-29 16:51  juanco

	* test/data/parsing/conditionals/: final/should_1.txt,
	final/should_2.txt, final/should_3.txt, build.xml (utags:
	v_0_1_109, v_0_1_3, v_0_1_31, v_0_1_4, v_0_1_0_base): Added
	external test for build script conditionals.

2001-04-29 16:49  juanco

	* src/: elements/TimeElements.pas, tasks/EchoTasks.pas,
	tasks/ExecTasks.pas: Updated element registration to new
	RegisterElements format.
	
	Fixed logs which were either to verbose or did not apply
	ToRelativePath to logged file paths.

2001-04-29 16:47  juanco

	* src/lib/clutilfile.pas: Made TclFileCompare.CompareFiles be a
	class function so it can be easily called without instantiating the
	object.

2001-04-29 16:45  juanco

	* make/bootstrap.bat: Made dcc32 call in bootstrap.bat again be
	quiet

2001-04-29 16:45  juanco

	* want.xml, src/tasks/DelphiTasks.pas, test/DelphiTasksTest.pas:
	Changes to <dcc> task. Renamed dcus to dcuoutput, exes to
	exeoutput, unit to unitpath, resource to resourcepath, include to
	includepath.
	
	With new version of patternsets, path elements support refid as an
	attribute, and buils cripts  can be less verbose: <unitpath
	refid="sources" />.
	
	Updated dante's build.xml to match <dcc> task changes.

2001-04-29 16:41  juanco

	* src/elements/PatternSets.pas: Added support for refid as
	attribute to filesets. That is: <fileset refid="apatternsetname" 
	/>

2001-04-29 16:39  juanco

	* test/ExternalTests.pas: Made TDanteExternalTest support test
	directories in which the setup and final dirs are expanded in
	directories instead of zipped.
	
	Made TDanteExternalTest report the file names of files for which
	the content did not match.

2001-04-29 16:37  juanco

	* src/WantClasses.pas: Added support for conditionals if= and
	unless=. Aliased the conditionals to ifdef= and ifndef=, to make
	Delphi programmers happy.
	
	Refactored RegisterElement and friends so the parent element is the
	first paramenter and the child elements are listed in the second.
	This makes RegisterElement calls look more like syntax definitions,
	which is sort of what they are.

2001-04-28 03:25  juanco

	* doc/: style.css (tags: v_0_1_31, v_0_1_4, v_0_1_3, v_0_1_0_base),
	task_writers_guide.html: Fixed bugs still present in the Task
	Writers Guide. Also updated it to the latest version of Dante's
	core classes and methods.

2001-04-28 02:14  juanco

	* want.xml: Changes to build.xml according to suggestions by Andrew
	Smith.
	
	Set uselibrarypath=false in all <dcc> instances, and make all
	targets that use <dcc> depend on the 'clean' target. This should
	avoid conflicts with user setups and let us detect if something got
	out of wack while compiling with the IDE.
	
	Other changes:
	
	Cleaned up the "dist" task. Used generic wildcards to make sure
	that all .zips in the ./lib directory are included, but none of the
	./lib subdirectories are.
	
	The 'clean' target will not remove the 'dist' directory. This
	change should let Chris accumulate release .zips in his hard disk.
	
	The 'clean' target removes files in the ./dcu directory but does
	not remove the directory.  This change was done to avoid having the
	target file while trying to remove ./dcu.  The ./dcu directory
	contained CVS files in early snapshots, and those are ignored by
	the file tasks by default. Gave same treatment to the ./bin
	directory.

2001-04-27 21:39  juanco

	* private/juanco/todo_juanco.html: Updated juanco's todo list

2001-04-27 21:37  juanco

	* doc/authors.txt: Added e-mail address to Juanco's entry.

