	* test/VssTasksTest.pas: Changed TProject.Level back to
	TProject.Verbosity

2001-04-27 12:58  chrismo

	* src/dante.dpr: fixed typo in comment

2001-04-27 12:57  chrismo

	* doc/authors.txt: no message

2001-04-27 01:13  juanco

	* src/: lib/LogMgr.pas, win32/ConsoleListener.pas: Patches so
	console log manager works under Win9x

2001-04-26 21:39  juanco

	* src/tasks/ExecTasks.pas: Try to detect runnaway applications in
	<exec>

2001-04-26 21:37  juanco

	* src/ScriptRunner.pas: Avoid logging EDanteExceptions twice

