2001-04-23 22:47  juanco

	* src/tasks/ZipTasks.pas: Reversed change that made <zip> honor
	basedirs of its <filesets>. The change prevented the use of
	<fileset> as a partitioning deviced because it made the .zip dir
	structure not match the actual dir structure. What we really need
	is a way to make <zip> open existing files without scratching them.

