2001-04-23 20:49  chrismo

	* src/tasks/vsstasks.pas: Oops ... forgot to register the new tasks

2001-04-23 20:49  chrismo

	* src/tasks/FileTasks.pas: Delete task now has a DeleteReadOnly
	property allowing read-only files to be deleted if set to true.
	
	I also removed the requirement for the Delete task to have either
	the file or dir property set. If I want to delete all files in a
	directory, I can include a FileSet and don't want to delete a
	specific file or directory in that case. The task was already coded
	to actually do this work, but the Init wouldn't allow it to be used
	this way.

2001-04-23 20:47  chrismo

	* src/lib/WildPaths.pas: MoveFile calls Windows.MoveFile instead of
	MoveFileEx since ...Ex isn't implemented on Win9x.
	
	Added to DeleteFile to allow DeleteReadOnly parameter.

