	* want.xml, make/bootstrap.bat: Updated bootstrap and build.xml to
	use conditional compile directives in test.dprs .

2001-04-23 14:37  chrismo

	* test/VssTasksTest.pas: Vss testing now will do purging and is
	much cleaner. Tests for Checkout and Checkin task objects.

2001-04-23 14:35  chrismo

	* test/: DanteAcceptTest.dpr, DanteTest.dpr: Changed IsConsole with
	conditional compile. Linker settings create a console for Dante to
	be able to function with GUITestRunner -- and this sets IsConsole
	to true which disables using GUITestRunner.
	
	Conditional compile allows Dante's build.xml to run the TextRunner
	from the command line during a build while still keeping
	GUITestRunner an option from the IDE.

