2001-04-20 23:08  juanco

	* test/RunnerTests.pas: BUG: TTestDanteMain would fail randomly
	because it didn't guard against <shell> exit codes. Fixed.

2001-04-20 20:46  juanco

	* src/lib/WildPaths.pas (tags: added_color): WildPath wildcards can
	now contain a comma-separated list of patterns.

2001-04-20 20:26  juanco

	* src/: dante.dof, dante.dpr: Moved build file name functionality
	out of DanteClasses and into DanteMain and dante.dpr.
	
	A search for a build file is done only if the -buildfile option was
	not used. This behavior is consistent with Ant.
	
	The default build file name is AppName.xml, where AppName is the
	name of the .exe used to invoke the tool. This lets users that have
	added custom tasks to the tool use a different file name just by
	renaming the .exe.
	
	If the search for the AppName.xml fails, then the tool searches for
	dante.xml. If that fails, then the tool searches for build.xml
	(this is for backwards compatibility).

2001-04-20 20:13  juanco

	* src/: ScriptRunner.pas, WantClasses.pas, tasks/WantTasks.pas:
	Moved build file name functionality out of DanteClasses and into
	DanteMain and dante.dpr.
	
	A search for a build file is done only if the -buildfile option was
	not used. This behavior is consistent with Ant.
	
	The default build file name is AppName.xml, where AppName is the
	name of the .exe used to invoke the tool. This lets users that have
	added custom tasks to the tool use a different file name just by
	renaming the .exe.
	
	If the search for the AppName.xml fails, then the tool searches for
	dante.xml. If that fails, then the tool searches for build.xml
	(this is for backwards compatibility).

