2001-04-16 23:55  juanco

	* want.xml, src/ScriptRunner.pas, src/WantClasses.pas,
	src/dante.dof, src/dante.dpr, src/elements/PatternSets.pas,
	src/elements/Properties.pas (tags: added_color),
