	test/RunnerTests.pas, test/WantClassesTest.pas: Removed
	dependencies from core classes to TComponent. Use new TTree
	(OwnedTrees.pas) instead.
	
	Implemented element registry that allows, among other things,
	changing build.xml syntax from user modules.
	
	Implemented the task registry using the element registry.
	
	Moved use of StandardTasks, CustomTasks, and StandardElements into
	DanteMain.pas.
	
