	<patternset> and <property> elements out of DanteClasses and into
	their own units, Patternsets.pas and Properties.pas
	
	Merged FileSets.pas into Patternsets.pas.
	
	Renamed TDanteElement.XMLTag to TagName.
	
	Added a <regexp> element using PerlRE 1.1. Added simple test case.
	
	All tests except those for VSS to 100%.

