2001-03-23 19:58  chrismo

	* src/tasks/ExecTasks.pas, test/ExecTasksTest.pas: In
	TCustomExecTask.BuildCmdLine, removed Arguments.CommaText and
	replaced with simple loop. CommaText interferes with strings with
	spaces and what not. See the unit tests for details.

